altTitles.en: Shut up and take my money!
Take My Money  [รักนี้...มีเปย์!]

description.en:
One day Mina, a rich student who's both beautiful and popular, falls in love with an upperclassman. Even through Mina's countless efforts of using money to get the upperclassman's heart, the prince's heart won't budge. 

Can Mina's one-sided love story be successful?
